quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  92,1,Mi woondarii jemma si mbo arii e niɓɓidde
  92,2,O woondirii ñalawma sombo hunciima
  92,3,O woondirii ko O tagi ko gorel e deyel
  92,4,Pellet golle mon na ceerti
  92,5,Tawi ko oon tottirɗo o reenti
  92,6,O goonɗini baraaji golle mum
  92,7,Ma Min newnan mbo kala jam e newaare. @Corrected
  92,8,Tawi ko oon ngammbuɗo o yondinii
  92,9,O fenni njoɓdi
  92,10,Ma Min newnan mbo satteende. @Corrected
  92,11,Nafataa mbo jawdi makko si o saami e yiite
  92,12,Ko e Amen peewal woni
  92,13,Ko minen woodani nguurndam cakkitiɗam e ngadiɗam
  92,14,Njeertin Mi mon yiite huɓɓoowe
  92,15,Naatataange si wona ɓurɗo hiiteede
  92,16,Oon pennuɗo ɗuurnii
  92,17,Ma woɗɗita ngol ɓurɗo reentaade oon woni Abu Bakri yo welu Alla won e makko
  92,18,Oon tottiroowo jawdi makko ngam o laaɓa
  92,19,Alanah hay gooto ka Makko neemo joɓeteeɗo
  92,20,Tawi wonah ɗaɓɓude Alla ɓurɗo toowde O
  92,21,Yaama o wele